  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3576750/extras/3d86322a824d00ffab05251d500c7c77.poster.avif?t=1745417111\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3576750/extras/3d86322a824d00ffab05251d500c7c77.webm?t=1745417111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3576750/extras/3d86322a824d00ffab05251d500c7c77.mp4?t=1745417111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>It Was Beautiful is an emotional adventure where you embark on a journey with a little fish striving to fulfill its final wish. After learning about its terminal illness and limited time, it sets out to witness the mysterious sunset depicted in an old painting. Together with its father, the fish heads toward the water's surface, hoping for a miracle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3576750/extras/57dba7625e48dd95d9b6485b5b967aef.poster.avif?t=1745417111\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3576750/extras/57dba7625e48dd95d9b6485b5b967aef.webm?t=1745417111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3576750/extras/57dba7625e48dd95d9b6485b5b967aef.mp4?t=1745417111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- A Deep Story – Immerse yourself in a touching narrative exploring themes of life, hope, and acceptance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Atmospheric Graphics – Enjoy stunning underwater landscapes filled with mysteries and uncharted places.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Character Relationships – Experience warmth and support in the bond between the protagonist and their father.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Puzzles & Exploration – Solve challenges and explore a world where every decision may lead to a meaningful discovery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The Mysterious Sunset – Pursue a symbol of beauty and hope that may change the way you see life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The Flow of Time – Feel the weight of every fleeting moment in a world where time is slipping away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It Was Beautiful is a game about finding beauty in a world full of hardships and unknown horizons. Embark on a journey filled with hope and discover the strength to believe in miracles.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3576750/extras/3d86322a824d00ffab05251d500c7c77.poster.avif?t=1745417111\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3576750/extras/3d86322a824d00ffab05251d500c7c77.webm?t=1745417111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3576750/extras/3d86322a824d00ffab05251d500c7c77.mp4?t=1745417111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>It Was Beautiful is an emotional adventure where you embark on a journey with a little fish striving to fulfill its final wish. After learning about its terminal illness and limited time, it sets out to witness the mysterious sunset depicted in an old painting. Together with its father, the fish heads toward the water's surface, hoping for a miracle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3576750/extras/57dba7625e48dd95d9b6485b5b967aef.poster.avif?t=1745417111\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3576750/extras/57dba7625e48dd95d9b6485b5b967aef.webm?t=1745417111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3576750/extras/57dba7625e48dd95d9b6485b5b967aef.mp4?t=1745417111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- A Deep Story – Immerse yourself in a touching narrative exploring themes of life, hope, and acceptance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Atmospheric Graphics – Enjoy stunning underwater landscapes filled with mysteries and uncharted places.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Character Relationships – Experience warmth and support in the bond between the protagonist and their father.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Puzzles & Exploration – Solve challenges and explore a world where every decision may lead to a meaningful discovery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The Mysterious Sunset – Pursue a symbol of beauty and hope that may change the way you see life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The Flow of Time – Feel the weight of every fleeting moment in a world where time is slipping away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It Was Beautiful is a game about finding beauty in a world full of hardships and unknown horizons. Embark on a journey filled with hope and discover the strength to believe in miracles.</p>",
